{"type":null,"faqId":45344,"title":"荣耀盒子M321的红外遥控器与家中其他设备的遥控器串号怎么办？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 1  </span><span>用红外遥控器控制一个设备前，请将另一个设备关机并断电。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 2  </span><span>如果不方便将另一个设备关机，请将会发生串号的两个设备分开放置，并用障碍物隔开。遥控时，将红外遥控器靠近并对准需要控制的设备。并远离另一个设备。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164860\" style=\"width:0.93680555in;height:0.43680555in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>需要特别注意的是，当荣耀立方离荣耀盒子M321很近，且正在工作。如果此时您用红外遥控器控制盒子。很可能荣耀立方也在默默地响应着您的遥控。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":246,"faqType":"遥控","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"865","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Remote","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442556875000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M321,MediaQ M321-20","visitedTimes":10,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"红外,遥控,串号,荣耀盒子","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}